    <div class="info-section">
      <p>At Stumps Cricket, our mission is simple: to re-energise cricket in the UK. We deliver exciting, modern and inclusive coaching programmes designed to inspire players of every age and ability. Whether someone is picking up a bat for the very first time, sharpening their skills for club cricket, or striving for higher-level performance, we create an environment that sparks passion, confidence and growth.</p>
      <div class="section-content">
        <p>Put feature content here</p>
      </div>
